</title>
<subSubSection id="0B8093B8A41CF7E3BC8A891D8DC8E8E8" pageId="null" pageNumber="110" type="description">
<paragraph id="CCC0FBC6E958D6A397C6511F850BF83D" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">
Kelch 
<normalizedToken id="FCAC6A678F64A2AABD8914B7B2462452" originalValue="glockenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">glockenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, 2lippig; 
<emphasis id="74777CB446C21C73DD56E108F1435DB9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">
Oberlippe 
<normalizedToken id="E837EBCF262E9885D01FC8B1CA35C6FC" originalValue="groß" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">gross</normalizedToken>
, rundlich, ungeteilt, mit an der 
<normalizedToken id="90735DA86C553054BFDF0572A3B0E146" originalValue="Röhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Roehre</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="7D4AF704658281FA9988B2C3C17E5644" originalValue="flügelförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">fluegelfoermig</normalizedToken>
herablaufenden 
<normalizedToken id="127C8FCA417E0F8BD111EE6E2641890B" originalValue="Rändern" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Raendern</normalizedToken>
; Unterlippe 4 
<normalizedToken id="26A0E4A03313F2F8EEAD0A6D8EE8C01C" originalValue="zähnig" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">zaehnig</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Krone mit kurzer 
<normalizedToken id="634CA33D27F387A87373E183C8672AD4" originalValue="Röhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Roehre</normalizedToken>
und 2lippigem Rand; 
<emphasis id="CF04B924C4F9DF4463054E5F91343CDD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Oberlippe mit 4</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="DD26DE8E1809535D26FD3B44117CDA6C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">
5 stumpfen 
<normalizedToken id="FB3DF1BE9DF449EC9028BE79B6139866" originalValue="Zähnen" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Zaehnen</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, 
<normalizedToken id="565C5911D02D4ECF70E53E07E387E3BA" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">+/-</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="7E764C716B46F8C1AB1AA37B87EF3B7D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">flach, nicht gebogen; Unterlippe ganzrandig.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="A0D199160464AC7493A53EC20B4AC9A7" originalValue="Staubblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Staubblaetter</normalizedToken>
4, parallel, 
<emphasis id="4E102CA2512B34D03C43154D7F8A8E72" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">auf die Unterlippe herabgebogen</emphasis>
, mit parallelen 
<normalizedToken id="2366770FBAE8536E8C30010A3AAB02C0" originalValue="Staubbeutelhälften" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Staubbeutelhaelften</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="39F17D0872D5E0E30F2330F636698E07" originalValue="Teilfrüchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Teilfruechte</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="F260468C42D6D06C0958533AAA706CA5" originalValue="eiförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">eifoermig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8E433004C3076F04AEB7EF305721ABA0" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">
Die Gattung 
<emphasis id="0BC6862871EE821052723BB6E04BAF33" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">
<taxonomicName id="E3A6BF586A3E7E07038D0CA3686951AE" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Ocimum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="110" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Ocimum</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="9CA7974F166AE9DC5227485A5640087D" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">umfasst</normalizedToken>
etwa 60 Arten
</emphasis>
, die vor allem in den 
<emphasis id="A2D64C454F78280FE893B4C0D008A56C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="110">Tropen</emphasis>
verbreitet sind.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
